<h3>
CfP: ALA Conference 2015, &quot;African Futures and Beyond. Visions in Transition&quot;
</h3>
</div>
<div class='well'>
<p class=''>
<b>
Ort:
</b>
Bayreuth
</p>
<p class=''>
<b>
Frist:
</b>
2014-11-30
</p>
<p class=''>
<b>
Beginn:
</b>
2015-06-03
</p>
<p class=''>
<b>
